cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on using synthetic data to improve the accuracy of neural networks for action categorization. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the use of synthetic data for training neural networks is a common technique in the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
